description:
A sneak peek at @parispaloma 's single for The Lord of the Rings: The War of the Rohirrim! Been super curious to hear how they might carry on the tradition of end credits songs!

Full song drops on December 14th - the day after the film premieres.

#waroftherohirrim #parispaloma #lordoftherings
title: "The Rider" by Paris Paloma from The War of the Rohirrim Sneak Peek
